ERRORS:
--------


- error:
CAUSE: THE BELOW ERROR CAUSED DUE TO MISCONFIGURATION OF SECRET ATTRIBUTE IN THE MANIFEST AT THE "VOLUMEMOUNT" OF THE "KANIKO" CONTAINER

pod.yaml(WRONG)
-------------
  initContainers:
    - name: kaniko
      image: bitnami/kaniko
      args:
        - "--dockerfile=/space/app/multi_mvn_tom_settings"
        - "--context=/space/app"
        - "--destination=heartocean/pvt:spring1"
      volumeMounts:
        - name: vol1
          mountPath: /space/app
        - name: docker-secr
          mountPath: /kaniko
  volumes:
    - name: docker-secr
      secret:
        secretName: docker-cred
        items:
          - key: .dockerconfigjson
            path: config.json
-------------

pod.yaml(CORRECT)
------------
  initContainers:
    - name: kaniko
      image: bitnami/kaniko
      args:
        - "--dockerfile=/space/app/multi_mvn_tom_settings"
        - "--context=/space/app"
        - "--destination=heartocean/pvt:spring1"
      volumeMounts:
        - name: vol1
          mountPath: /space/app
        - name: docker-secr
          mountPath: /kaniko/.docker/
  volumes:
    - name: docker-secr
      secret:
        secretName: docker-cred
        items:
          - key: .dockerconfigjson
            path: config.json
-------------


